text: Will you also come along, Producer?

Yeah, it's an unfamiliar city after all,
I'd be worried letting you go out on your own.
And I have no idea where you might wonder off to, Mamimi...

Well, if you're with me Producer,
that'll be fun in it's own way I'm sure.
Speaking of which, this is the place.

Oh, you had somewhere in mind that you wanted to go to?
You know a lot despite this being your first name around here.

Yeah,
I scoped this place out before we came.

Wow, you thought about that sort of thing...
As expect... you make it seem so easy...
